Description:

Today we will pay a small tribute to the letter "T".
Given an integer n, print a letter "T" of height n.

Input: 5, 7, 4

TTTTT
  T
  T
  T
  T

TTTTTTT
   T
   T
   T
   T
   T
   T

TT TT
  T
  T
  T
  T
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Program:

To try this program, just run: "php YourFileDirectory/LetterT.php" 
on the terminal and voila!

